## xfceExt.sys

##################################
#### XFCE
#################################

SetEnv WM_DIR $[HOME]/.fvwm/wmEXT
SetEnv HOME_DIR $[HOME]/.fvwm

## No title
Style *Whisker* NoTitle
Style *xfce4-panel* NoTitle

KillModule FvwmButtons TaskButtonsFlux

KillModule FvwmButtons DashToDock
Read $[EXTRA_DIR]/MODULES/DashToDock/action/north.conf
*hideBar: Geometry 533x6-546+15
*DashToDock: Geometry 525x48-550+17

*ControlPanelB: Geometry 360x39-91+27
